This directory contains comprehensive TypeScript type definitions for a TODO application with React state management.

## Files Overview

- **`todo.ts`** - Core Todo interface and related input/update types
- **`filters.ts`** - Filter types for viewing todos (all, active, completed)
- **`actions.ts`** - Action types for state management with Redux-style patterns
- **`state.ts`** - Application state interface and selectors
- **`utils.ts`** - Utility types and helper functions
- **`react.ts`** - React component prop types and hook interfaces
- **`index.ts`** - Barrel file exporting all types

